OL,3,CIndustry warns proposed gambling tax
OL,4,Crises would cost up to 40,000 jobs
OL,6,FThe IPPR estimates the Chancellor
OL,7,Fcould raise #3.2 billion a year in her
OL,8,FBudget if:
OL,10,F Remote Gambling Duty on online
OL,11,Fslots, poker, and online bingo rises
OL,12,Ffrom 21% to 50%.
OL,14,F Machine Games Duty on cash-prize
OL,15,Fslot machines rises from 20% to 50%.
OL,17,F General Betting Duty on sports
OL,18,Fbetting (excluding horse racing),
OL,19,Fonline or in betting shops, rises from
OL,20,F15% to 30%.
