OL,3,CIndustry warns proposed gambling tax
OL,4,Crises would cost up to 40,000 jobs
OL,6,F2. It fails to include the impact of
OL,7,Fthe recent White Paper reforms, which
OL,8,FEY argues will cut online gambling
OL,9,Frevenues by around #725 million a year.
OL,11,F3. It overestimates the future growth
OL,12,Fof online gambling.
OL,14,FLast week, BetFred warned that tax
OL,15,Frises on the scale advocated by the
OL,16,FIPPR would force the closure of its
OL,17,F1,300 betting shops, with the loss of
OL,18,F7,000 jobs.
OL,20,FGreg Knight, who runs JenningsBet, has
OL,21,Ftold ITV News he has the same concerns.
