OL,3,CIndustry warns proposed gambling tax
OL,4,Crises would cost up to 40,000 jobs
OL,6,FThe company operates around 150
OL,7,Fbetting shops in the UK and employs
OL,8,Fjust over 1,000 people. Last year,
OL,9,FJenningsBet paid almost #17.5 million
OL,10,Fin gambling duties and levies.
OL,12,F"This is existential," Knight said.
OL,13,F"The increase in Machine Gaming Duty
OL,14,Falone would wipe out any forecast
OL,15,Fprofit this year and we would be loss-
OL,16,Fmaking. It's clearly bonkers."
