OL,6,FIn a statement, Professor Ashwin
OL,7,FKumar, director of research and policy
OL,8,Fat IPPR, said: "Our report is an
OL,9,Findependent, evidence-based assessment
OL,10,Fof how the gambling sector can make a
OL,11,Ffairer contribution to society. It's
OL,12,Fno surprise that an industry lobbying
OL,13,Fgroup is opposed to higher taxes on
OL,14,Fits members, but their claims of
OL,15,Fpotential job losses and huge
OL,16,Fincreases in illegal gambling don't
OL,17,Fstand up to scrutiny.
